"{\"uid\": \"gbnews.com-sport-olympics-jack-carlin-update-team-gb-horror-crash-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PM speaks with Donald Trump just HOURS after President mocked Sir Keir  Jack Carlin seemed to be okay after being checked out by medics at the Paris Olympics on Sunday  GETTY  ByJack Otway,  Published: 11/08/2024  Updated: 11/08/2024  The 27-year-old has already won two medals at the games in France  Jack Carlin seemed to be okay after being checked out by medics at the Paris Olympics on Sunday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999596898314, \"rank\": 2.9058113165372023e-08, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Otway_National_Park\", \"score\": 0.919841332224643, \"rank\": 0.08703701453683253, \"text\": \"Otway\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Otway_National_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Otway_National_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9994353310764404, \"rank\": 0.00046470510293769563, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"score\": 0.7327668803267725, \"rank\": 0.3060248984725243, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\"}, {\"begin\": 307, \"end\": 313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\", \"score\": 0.9995454701984429, \"rank\": 0.0004547364928711759, \"text\": \"Carlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old cycling star was sent crashing to the floor after a three-man collision on the final lap of the men's keirin final.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 518, \"end\": 524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.463726402501988e-40, \"text\": \"keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carlin attempted to make a late play for bronze, having already won two medals out in France so far this summer.However, he ended up crashing to the deck after a collision between Japan's Shinji Nakano and Malaysia's Muhammad Shah Firdaus Sahrom just in front of him.Jack Carlin seemed to be okay after being checked out by medics at the Paris Olympics on Sunday|GETTYThere was concern for Carlin in the immediate aftermath of the crash.His skin suit was ripped and medics hurried over to treat him.Fortunately, Carlin was able to get back to his feet as he walked away from the scene with a look of frustration on his face.Medics offered to put a neck brace on the Team GB star but he politely declined that offer.JUST IN:Man Utd duo left furious with Andre Onana during Community Shield defeat to Man CityCarlin's crash means one of Team GB's last hopes for a gold medal is now over.He had previously been part of the side that claimed silver in the men's team sprint, while he also secured bronze in the individual sprint.The crash comes less than 24 hours after Ollie Wood was also involved in a scary collision.The 28-year-old was headbutted by a rival while competing in the madison final, with the Netherlands' Jan Willem van Schip disqualified.READ MORE:Gabby Logan brands Olympics star 'selfish' in stinging attack live on BBCAnd Wood admitted he felt like a 'crash test dummy' after the crash, with the Team GB star saying: \\\"He hit me so hard.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 533, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\", \"score\": 0.9995454701984429, \"rank\": 0.0004547364928711759, \"text\": \"Carlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\"}, {\"begin\": 619, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9994353310764404, \"rank\": 0.00046470510293769563, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 713, \"end\": 718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.8649794792711998, \"rank\": 0.1504784285315354, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 721, \"end\": 734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shinji_Nakano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shinji Nakano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shinji_Nakano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shinji_Nakano\"}, {\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"score\": 0.9964639225329484, \"rank\": 0.002896311059137065, \"text\": \"Malaysia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\"}, {\"begin\": 750, \"end\"